title: Foreign Minister Kaljurand opened the new Embassy building in London (Ministry of Foreign Affairs of ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Estonia ) Today , on October 14 , Foreign Minister Marina Kaljurand opened the new building of the Estonian Embassy in the Kensington and Chelsea district at 44 Queen's Gate Terrace .
